	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hmm...Miragul is also the Necro responsible for creating Shakey Scarecrow in Rivervale.&nbsp;&nbsp;I doubt this particular item is related to that quest, but it is interesting that step one of that quest (either incomplete or unsolved) is chasing down documentation on HOW to fix Shakey's head.  <br><br>That starts you in Erudin and buys you a slip of paper, that references Miragul.  No one is quite sure where it goes from there but game background documentation gives you a nice bio of Miragul and says he lived in Paineel at one point.  Have thought about chasing down places where he had lived to see if I could find any other slips of paper, but sigh could it be this item that is needed?<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
