	   <tr><td colspan=2>my raid-group on erollisi marr has been *very* busy looking into this item's past =)<br><br>it is not a book the oracle wants, looking over it all he only wants the book of turmoil and of scale just yet still.&nbsp;&nbsp;and he's pretty specific about the titles of the books he wants.<br><br>we are thinking it is related to the present gm-event across all servers, and was an item given to miragul by trakanon.  we believe dartain the lost was miragul's apprentice.  giving the book to miragul is probably not going to do anything...  though it wouldn't hurt to try =)<br><br>the tome allowed miragul to become as powerful as he became... but miragul is done with.  the second and third artifacts trakanon gave his chosen are more likely to be productive, since the second chosen may still be living, and the third item trakanon may want back.<br><br>charmian d`arxx, conjurer of the cimmerii, erollisi marr server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
