	   <tr><td colspan=2>I picked this interesting little item up last night in The Hole.&nbsp;&nbsp;After a little discussing among guildmates, I managed to convince them to head out to OOT with me to go see the oracle out there to see if this was for helping bypass part of the paladin epic since verant put in some steps for several other classes recently for their epics.  Well turning it in to the oracle didn't do anything, so we smacked him around like a red-headed step child, picked my book back up and we'll go take a look over at Miragul a little later this week.  Wish me luck, and post if you've gotten any info to help out on this.<br><br>Norfolk Peacebringer<br>57th Knight<br>Ayonae Ro<br>Mithril Tower<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
